title: Kreator - 2005 - Enemy Of God [320kbs] ~~Renovatio~~
description:
Enemy of God is the eleventh studio album by German thrash metal band Kreator. The gothenburg influences of the band's previous album, Violent Revolution, became more prominent on this album. 

It was released by Steamhammer Records on January 10 in Europe and South America and on January 11, 2005 in North America. On October 27, 2006, the album was re-released in a digipak under the name "Enemy of God: Revisited", with a 5.1 DTS 96/24 mix, featuring two bonus tracks from the Japanese edition and a bonus DVD.
